properties.areaDesc: Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 19 at 3:02AM EST until January 20 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds near 20 kt gusting to 25 to 30 kt and seas 6
to 8 feet expected.

* WHERE...Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...From 3 AM to 4 PM Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 4 PM MONDAY
